defaultexploration/testing boreholes
default in 2010 and 2012:-
default              
default(a)
default              
defaultWrexham (A/10/2122444): Main issues = the effects of traffic, noise and disturbance on local residents. 
default              
default(b)
default              
defaultVale of Glamorgan (A/11/2167112): Main issues = the effects upon the quantity and quality of groundwater supplies in the area. 
